  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Assistance - Country-Level Funding - IOM 2019</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Activities under this project aim to contribute towards a more informed and coordinated humanitarian response in displacement sites in the Ituri province, as well as to improve the living conditions and protection of the most vulnerable internally displaced persons. This will be achieved through two main activities;  the collection and analysis of accurate and timely displacement data to support well-informed coordination, response planning and assistance to displaced populations and the improved access to basic services and protection through sustained humanitarian coordination and site management.</narrative>
  </description>
